OL,3,CGrenfell Tower: Injured firefighters
OL,4,Chave settled High Court case
OL,6,FFirefighters who were injured in the
OL,7,FGrenfell Tower fire have settled High
OL,8,FCourt claims for a total of #20
OL,9,Fmillion.
OL,11,FThe Fire Brigades Union (FBU) said
OL,12,Fsome of the 114 firefighters involved
OL,13,Fhad not been able to work again
OL,14,Fbecause of "severe trauma" following
OL,15,Fthe blaze in June 2017.
OL,17,FDefendants included companies that
OL,18,Fmade the tower block's cladding and
OL,19,Fthe Royal Borough of Kensington and
OL,20,FChelsea and the London Fire
OL,21,FCommissioner.
