OL,6,FThe fire at the residential tower
OL,7,Fblock in North Kensington, west
OL,8,FLondon, on 14th June 2017 killed 72
OL,9,Fpeople.
OL,11,FMatt Wrack, Fire Brigades Union
OL,12,Fgeneral secretary, said: "The
OL,13,Faftermath of the Grenfell Tower
OL,14,Ftragedy is a stark reminder of the
OL,15,Fsystemic failings of building safety
OL,16,Fand government accountability.
OL,18,F"Firefighters, many of whom have been
OL,19,Fdeeply affected by the horrors they
OL,20,Fwitnessed, continue to advocate for
OL,21,Fthose living in unsafe conditions.
