OL,6,FThe blaze was the deadliest in the
OL,7,FUnited Kingdom since the Second World
OL,8,FWar, resulting in 72 deaths and
OL,9,Fleaving many residents injured and
OL,10,Fhomeless. The public inquiry into the
OL,11,Fblaze is expected to publish its final
OL,12,Freport this year.
OL,14,FHe added: "This was a crime of
OL,15,Fderegulation and negligence ` a
OL,16,Fconsequence of private profit being
OL,17,Fprioritised over public safety. Nearly
OL,18,Fseven years later, the fight for
OL,19,Fjustice and change goes on.
OL,26,@vD@KOU
