OL,4,Chave settled High Court case
OL,6,F"The Fire Brigades Union stands
OL,7,Fshoulder to shoulder with the victims
OL,8,Fand survivors of Grenfell Tower, and
OL,9,Fwith leaseholders and campaign groups
OL,10,Facross the UK."
OL,12,FVincent Reynolds from the personal
OL,13,Finjury team at Thompsons Solicitors,
OL,14,Fwhich represented the firefighters,
OL,15,Fsaid: "The Grenfell Tower fire left an
OL,16,Findelible mark on the firefighters who
OL,17,Fresponded to the call.
