OL,3,CGrenfell Tower: Injured firefighters
OL,4,Chave settled High Court case
OL,6,F"Many bear the psychological scars of
OL,7,Fthat night, struggling with trauma
OL,8,Ffrom the harrowing experience. Their
OL,9,Ftestimonies reveal the profound
OL,10,Fpersonal sacrifice of showing such
OL,11,Fextraordinary courage in the face of
OL,12,Fan impossible situation."
OL,14,FHe added: "The incident exposed them
OL,15,Fto unimaginable scenes and sparked a
OL,16,Fdeeper reflection on fire and building
OL,17,Fsafety policy.
