OL,6,F"Their experiences on that night, and
OL,7,Fin its aftermath, highlight the human
OL,8,Felement of firefighting, underscoring
OL,9,Ftheir commitment to their duty despite
OL,10,Fthe immense risks and emotional toll.
OL,12,F"We hope this settlement brings
OL,13,Fclosure of a sort for these
OL,14,Ffirefighters, although we know that
OL,15,Ffor many, the injuries will be for a
OL,16,Flifetime."
